The IronMic Story

In our process of creating podcasts, we faced a significant problem: there was no easy way to create a website for our podcast without paying for an expensive solution or spending a lot of time crafting a website of our own.

We built IronMic to solve that pain point by creating the easiest possible way to create a professional website for any podcast. With an RSS feed, you can automatically build a website that stays updated with new episodes.

IronMic was founded in the summer of 2018 by Sunny Singh, Kyle McDonald, and Leon Hitchens, who all share their take on the podcasting world. We host our podcast called IronMic’d, where we sit down and talk about the best ways to grow a podcast. Join us in our journey as we share our experience and services with the community.
